ZH: 我立在门口等你。
EN: I stand at the door waiting for you.

ZH: 他们立着面对彼此。
EN: They stand facing each other.

ZH: 孩子们在操场上立成一排。
EN: The children stand in a line on the playground.

ZH: 他们立在阳光下。
EN: They stand in the sunlight.

ZH: 我喜欢在雨中立着。
EN: I enjoy standing in the rain.

ZH: 她立在窗前注视着外面。
EN: She stands by the window looking outside.

ZH: 昨晚他们立在大厅里聊天。
EN: Last night they stood chatting in the hall.

ZH: 公司经理立着给员工讲话。
EN: The company manager stands giving a speech to the employees.

ZH: 他有一个习惯：每天早上醒来后第一件事就是立起来。
EN: He has a habit: the first thing he does every morning after waking up is standing up.

ZH: 请你立在这里不要动。
EN: Please stand still here and don't move.

ZH: 她立着，凝视着我的眼睛。
EN: She stands, gazing into my eyes.

ZH: 我们在大庭广众之中立了七八个小时。
EN: We stood in the midst of the crowd for seven or eight hours.

ZH: 他们立在河边看日落。
EN: They stand by the river watching the sunset.

ZH: 我们一起立在草地上欣赏夜空。
EN: We stand together on the grass to admire the night sky.

ZH: 请别动，保持站立状态。
EN: Please don't move, keep standing.

ZH: 在深山里立着，可以听见鸟鸣声。
EN: Standing in the deep mountains, you can hear the chirping of birds.

ZH: 我们一起立在高山上欣赏美丽风景。
EN: We stand together on the mountain to appreciate the beautiful scenery.

ZH: 这座古老的桥立在河边。
EN: This ancient bridge stands by the river.

ZH: 小猫一只腿立在早晨阳光里。
EN: The kitten stands on one leg in the morning sunlight.

ZH: 池塘里的鱼儿立着迎接第一缕阳光。
EN: The fish in the pond stand to welcome the first ray of sunlight.
